OFFICIAL AL-QAEDA RESPONSE
TO THE DEATH OF
ABU MUSAB AL-ZARQAWI
As long as there is
a Shiite mosque standing,
a market to bomb, or a
single infidel head left
to sever, we will continue
Allah's work.
